-- Bosch Plans to Acquire Conergy’s Voltwerk Division, FTD Reports
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2011-12-21T07:15:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-21/bosch-plans-to-acquire-conergy-s-voltwerk-division-ftd-reports.html
Robert Bosch GmbH plans to buy
 Conergy AG ’s Voltwerk unit under an agreement that may be
completed this week,  Financial Times Deutschland  reported today,
without saying where it obtained the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
